snippet.title: BACK TO SCHOOL GROCERY HAUL | Amber Eve
snippet.description:
Hiii everyone,

I'm a huge fan of Trader Joe's and thought I would show you guys what I usually get when I go grocery shopping! A lot of these items are perfect for those people who are on a budget, especially college students!

Hope you guys enjoy! Leave a comment on your favorite grocery item!!

xx Amber
_

ABOUT ME:

I am 22 year old college graduate from Massachusetts who loves filming and creating. I can’t wait to start posting content, as this is what I’ve been thriving to do for a long time! :)
